<body>
    <h1>🌟 Life in Deserts 🌵</h1>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>What is a Desert? 🤔</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>A place with very little rain and extreme weather.</li>
            <li>Two types: <strong>Hot</strong> (like Sahara) and <strong>Cold</strong> (like Ladakh).</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>🏜️ The Sahara Desert</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>World's largest hot desert, in Africa!</li>
            <li>Hot in the day, cold at night.</li>
            <li>People grow dates and live near oases.</li>
            <li>Animals: Camels, scorpions, and lizards.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>❄️ The Ladakh Desert</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Freezing cold desert in India.</li>
            <li>Known as the "Land of High Passes".</li>
            <li>People grow crops like barley and vegetables.</li>
            <li>Animals: Yaks, snow leopards, and mountain goats.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="fun-facts">
        <h2>Fun Facts 🎉</h2>
        <ul>
            <li> 🌵 Camels store fat in their humps, not water!</li>
            <li>🏔️ Ladakh has a double-humped camel called the Bactrian camel.</li>
            <li>🌞 The Sahara is bigger than the entire USA!</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
